{"tid":2267899,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"零售協會：23%會員料於12月起陸續裁員","createTime":"2020-11-02T11:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T13:21:00.000Z","uid":51665,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b9a91a2d418db48bf3ca27b2be2fd4c8196f58","tid":2267899,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1604314520070&amp;issue=20201102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1604314520070%26issue%3D20201102&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxViy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=58a489e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1604314520070&amp;issue=20201102</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20201102/s00010/55ec84c7fc8ffbd3120c93de06bf2f06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20201102%2Fs00010%2F55ec84c7fc8ffbd3120c93de06bf2f06.jpg&h=263bedd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港9月零售銷售按年下跌12.9%，略遜市場預期。香港零售管理協會主席謝邱安儀指出，首9個月累計已跌28.7%，由於去年下半年受社會運動影響，基數較低，相信第四季表現會好過28.7%的跌幅，如未有爆發疫情全年跌幅亦會相若或略為收窄。<br />\n<br />\n她又指，「保就業」計劃將於本月完結，預計零售商會陸續裁員，根據協會的調查，有23%受訪會員表示將於12月起裁員，幅度介乎輕微至15%。是次調查涉及20多個零售品牌，共有2800間分店及48000名員工，即最多或裁減約1600名員工。<br />\n<br />\n展望10月，謝邱安儀預計，將承接9月表現，由於去年基數較低，令跌幅稍為穩定。雖然限聚令有所放寬，市面人流增加，但購物意欲依然疲弱「旺丁不旺財」，未對零售業生意有很顯著幫助。<br />\n<br />\n儲錢移民吖嗱！穀種都無得你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b7f94639275c2155f5623722b2d9094abde6e5","tid":2267899,"uid":30476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"做埋聖誕做炒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c77461ad87ab57fbf0748180c6ae39c6f66362","tid":2267899,"uid":73991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:51:15.000Z","msg":"係真至好，唔好得個講字"},{"pid":"e265f00e5763737e4cc765d2b721203ce26bb8c6","tid":2267899,"ui